Title: Reference Manual
Author: Pistol Taeja
Format: Manga

# PAGE 1

Panel 1
This page is an example of an auto-arranged three panel layout.

In a MANGA format, every panel becomes a full-width strip, stacked top to bottom, read right to left.


    +-------------+
    |.....P1......|
    +-------------+
    |.....P2......|
    +-------------+
    |.....P3......|
    +-------------+

